IOS:
react-native bundle --entry-file index.js --bundle-output ios/main.jsbundle --dev=false --platform ios --assets-dest ios/

Android:
react-native bundle --platform android --dev false --entry-file index.js --bundle-output android/app/src/main/assets/index.android.bundle --assets-dest android/app/src/main/res/

Windows:
react-native bundle --platform windows --entry-file index.js --bundle-output windows\WoWsInfo\ReactAssets\index.windows.bundle --assets-dest windows\WoWsInfo\ReactAssets --dev false

Mac:
react-native-macos bundle --entry-file index.js --bundle-output macos/main.jsbundle --dev=false --platform macos --assets-dest macos/

REMEMBER:
REMEMBER TO CHANGE GITHUB_VERSIOn when making bundle for Google Play and IOS.